data.description: HUGE 2 STORY HOME-LOW TAXES AND NO HOA- RV PARKING- Welcome to your gorgeous 5 Bedroom Home, completely remodeled TOP TO BOTTOM in the last 2 years. This home is situated on a corner lot with a 3 car garage and a ton of driveway space to meet your parking needs. Stepping into the home you will notice an abundance of natural light, high ceilings, and an open layout. The entire home showcases Gray LVP and Plantation Shutters. Wow! The Formal Living and Dining Rooms are at the front of the home, flowing into the Family Room and Kitchen. You're going to love the impressive, custom fireplace in the Family Room and modern light fixture. The brand new Kitchen has been reconfigured to include additional cabinet space, a waterfall Island with seating for 3, white cabinets, stone counter tops with a striking gray vain, stainless appliances, a farmhouse sink, and tile backsplash. There is a walk in pantry too! There is 1 Bedroom and a full Bathroom downstairs with a step in shower. The massive Laundry room is downstairs, boasting a wash basin, cabinets, and extra room for you to add more cabinets or use as storage. Upstairs, you will find a cozy loft, which could be converted to a 6th Bedroom. There are 2 Bedrooms on 1 side of the hallway that share a Bathroom with a brand new dual sink vanity, new vanity light, new mirrors and faucets, low flow toilet, and a shower/tub combo. The spacious Primary Suite sits at the top of the stairs with another Bedroom right next to it. Wait until you see the Primary Bathroom! It feels like you're in a luxury hotel with its brand new tiled shower that includes a rain shower head, oversized soaking tub,  brand new dual sink vanities, new mirrors, new faucets, and a new light fixture. There is a walk in closet attached and a linen closet for you to enjoy! Downstairs, there are lovely French Doors leading to the back patio. It has a patio cover, the slope has been removed, and there is some turf that is perfect for pets to go potty. This low maintenance space has a rock flowerbed that is just waiting for your choice of flowers or trees to be planted. On the side yard is where you will find the deep and wide RV Parking with power hook ups. This exceptional home is in the highly rated Murrieta School District- it is just minutes to the 215 and 15 freeways, plus there is plenty of shopping and restaurants within a few miles. You don't want to miss out on this home! The remodel has been done for you! All you have to do is bring your stuff!
